data preparation.py: create x_windows.npy for 35040 dataset and use it for models' training
mixed_real_virtual_database.py: create 30% virtual data from original virtual dataset and 70% real data from original real dataset
100k data augmentation.py: augment the data from 35040 to 100k
100k x_windows formed.py: form x_windows_100k.npy for 100k data
100k authenticity.py: check if the data augmentation has a good quality 

models: 4 models for 35040 dataset and 4 models for 100k datasets
